name: üò± D√©couverte des donn√©es
query:
LOAD CSV WITH HEADERS FROM "file:///accidents-corporels-de-la-circulation-millesime.tsv" AS row FIELDTERMINATOR "\t"
RETURN row LIMIT 10

name: ‚ùóContraintes
query:
CREATE CONSTRAINT IF NOT EXISTS FOR (a:Accident) REQUIRE (a.accidentId) IS NODE KEY;
CREATE CONSTRAINT IF NOT EXISTS FOR (m:Manoeuvre) REQUIRE (m.manoeuvreId) IS NODE KEY;

name: üêé Chargement des Accidents
query:
LOAD CSV WITH HEADERS FROM "file:///accidents-corporels-de-la-circulation-millesime.tsv" AS row FIELDTERMINATOR "\t"
CALL {
  WITH row
  WITH row, [k in keys(row) | [apoc.text.camelCase(k), row[k]]] AS newPropPairs
  WITH row, apoc.map.fromPairs(newPropPairs) AS mapProps
  MERGE (a:Accident {accidentId: row.`Identifiant de l'accident`})
    ON CREATE SET a += mapProps
    ON MATCH SET a += mapProps
} IN TRANSACTIONS OF 100 rows

name: üêé Chargement Manoeuvres
query:
MATCH (a:Accident)
UNWIND split(a.man≈ìuvre, ",") AS manoeuvre
WITH DISTINCT manoeuvre
MERGE (m:Manoeuvre {manoeuvreId: manoeuvre})
